items.name: LEGO Star Wars Millennium Falcon" 75105
items.categoryPath: Sports & Outdoors/Sports Fan Shop/Baby Fan Shop/Baby Gear
items.shortDescription: One of the most iconic starships from Star Wars is back and the LEGO Star Wars Millennium Falcon 75105 is tougher than ever before. It was featured in exciting new scenes from Star Wars: The Force Awakens. This latest LEGO version of the Millennium Falcon is crammed with new and updated external features. This includes an even more streamlined and detailed design. The detachable cockpit has space for two minifigures because no pilot should be alone. This kids' play set has dual spring-loaded shooters, sensor dish, ramp and an entrance hatch ideal for imaginary fun. Open the hull plates to reveal even more new and updated details inside, including the main hold with seating area and holochess board. Another fantastic update is the even more detailed hyperdrive for any pocket-sized pilot on a mission.
items.longDescription: The secret compartment, extra boxes and cables, and storage for spring-loaded shooter ammo will help its legendary crew aboard the ship. Of course no LEGO Millennium Falcon model would be complete without crew members. Rey, Finn, Han Solo, Chewbacca, Tasu Leech and a Kanjiklub Gang Member, plus a BB-8 Astromech Droid are on board. items.name: LEGO Star Wars Snowspeeder
items.shortDescription: Add to your existing Rebel Alliance forces or start a new collection with the LEGO Star Wars Snowspeeder. This set features an agile Star Wars Snowspeeder Microfighter inspired by the vehicle that sped over the icy planet of Hoth in Episode V. The included LEGO Snowspeeder Microfighter features awesome details like a flick missile on each side and a mini cockpit. This miniature version of the Rebellion's super agile attack craft also includes a Snowspeeder Pilot to sit in the cockpit. The Snowspeeder Pilot minifigure is dressed in the iconic orange Rebel pilot flight suit and has a helmet and blaster. This LEGO Snowspeeder set makes an ideal display piece or addition to make-believe mini battles.

items.name: Star Wars Legendary Jedi Master Yoda
items.shortDescription: Learn from the best with a voice-activated Star Wars Legendary Jedi Master Yoda Figure that may be the most realistic Yoda ever produced. After eight hundred years of training, the beloved character has an eye for Jedi talent, and his eye is on you. The cool thing about this Star Wars figure is that you don't have to go all the way to the Jedi temple or crash-land in a swamp to take on menacing Sith lords who only think about themselves. This Yoda figure features 360 degree motorized movement over his entire body, along with full voice recognition software that almost quite literally brings him to life. In other words, this Star Wars collectible helps you walk the walk and talk the talk. Yoda also speaks 115 phrases, from classic bits of Jedi insight and wisdom to practical tips on how to deal with Sith lords, battle droids, and any other obstacles in your path.
items.longDescription: This Star Wars Legendary Jedi Master Yoda Figure operates in three separate modes, depending on your needs and your mood. He also uses his impressive Force Push powers to get his point across. This Star Wars figure comes complete with a light-up lightsaber and cane.<br><ul><li>Train to become a Jedi Master</li><li>360-degree motorized movement</li><li>Full voice recognition</li><li>Speaks 115 phrases</li><li>Includes Yoda figure, lightsaber and cane</li><li>3 modes of play: Force, Wisdom and Warrior</li><li>Star Wars collectible requires 6 C batteries (not included)</li></ul>

items.shortDescription: Add this LEGO Star Wars AT-AT to your child's toy collection. With this model, your little one can advance on the Rebel Hoth base. This LEGO Star Wars set features a small-scale version of the real Imperial Walker. It comes complete with a posable head and legs, two flick missiles and a mini cockpit for the driver to sit in. This mean Star Wars microfighter is going to take some stopping with its weapons and included blaster pistol. This item is designed for children aged 6 years and older. It can make a superb gift for any Star Wars fan or collector and also provide plenty of building fun.
